article_title: Newton Co. Distinguished Young Woman Chosen
article_text:
Seven young ladies competed Saturday night in Newton County's Distinguished Young Women Competition.

The girls were judged based on physical fitness, talent, an interview and an essay. Second alternate was awarded to Lucy Kastla, first alternate was Reagan Gorgas and the overall winner was Makaeya Brock. She will represent Newton County at the state program later this year.
